    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Thanks for the clarification.  In the beginning, I was sitting on the fence on whether I prefer the new cell to be automatically in edit mode.  But then I realized if I need to change the cell type, the fact that the cell is already in edit mode, doesn't hinder or slow my ability to change the cell type, so I don't see a con or negative when the cell is already in edit mode.\n"
